               stealing, on the <rs id="t18241028-130-cd687" type="crimeDate">23d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241028-130-off686 t18241028-130-cd687"></join>, two looking glasses, value 17 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18241028-130-victim1238" type="victimName">
