                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241028-130-victim1238 t18241028-130-viclabel691"></join>. I sent Spontini with the glasses to Duke-street, Manchester-square. The prisoner came to my house to buy one, and I had sent the two for his wife to see them.</p>
